{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 37,
  "title": "第三十七章（无名）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "道恆无名。侯王若守之，萬物將自化。化而欲作。吾將貞之以无名之樸。"
    },
    {
      "text": "貞之以无名之樸，夫將不辱。不辱以靜，天地將自正。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "道以無為為常也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 5,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言侯王若能守道，萬物將自化效於己也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 32,
          "end": 32
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "吾，身也。無明之樸，道德也。萬物已化效於己也。復欲作巧偽者，侯王當身鎮撫以道德也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "言侯王鎮撫以道德，民亦將不欲，故當以清靜導化之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 13,
          "end": 24
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "能如是者，天下將自正定也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "順自然也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 5,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "萬物無不由為以治以成之也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 32,
          "end": 32
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "化而欲作，作欲成也。吾將鎮之無名之樸，不為主也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 13
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "無欲競也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
